Adding Change Length of Stay Sub-KPI 25

Change Length of Stay




1. Click on an empty space on the canvas, and from the visualizations pane select Card.
2.Drag or select ‘ChangeLengthofStay’ into the Fields section.
3. Fill in the figures provided below for the necessary fields.
General:
Height=31
Width=71
Position,
Horizontal=145
Vertical=512
Title=Off
Effects =>
Background =Off
Boarder=off
Visual:
Callout Value =>
Font=DIN (15)
Font color=#000000
Decimal Place= 0
Category label=Off
